- Component Test creation MUST precede any code modification or creation
- Build and test execution REQUIRED after each development phase completion
- Code creation ONLY permitted after Component Test completion and validation
- Unit Test creation REQUIRED after Code implementation completion
- E2E Test creation REQUIRED after Unit Test completion and validation
- IMMEDIATE FAILURE required if any build or test step fails during cycle
- Follow exact TDD sequence without deviation or skipping phases
- Document test results and failures in artifacts folder for debugging